ul.li:
Kartézský součin dvou grafů \(G = {\color{lightgreen} G_1} \times {\color{orange} G_2}\):
\(V(G) = \left\{
({\color{lightgreen} x}, {\color{orange} y}) \mid
{\color{lightgreen} x} \in V(G_1),\ {\color{orange} y} \in V(G_2)
\right\}\)
\(\begin{matrix}
\begin{align}E(G) = & \big \{
\langle ({\color{lightgreen} x_1}, {\color{orange} y}), ({\color{lightgreen} x_2}, {\color{orange} y}) \rangle
\mid
\langle {\color{lightgreen} x_1}, {\color{lightgreen} x_2} \rangle \in E(G_1), {\color{orange} y} \in V(G_2) \}\\
\cup & \big \{
\langle ({\color{lightgreen} x}, {\color{orange} y_1}), ({\color{lightgreen} x}, {\color{orange} y_2}) \rangle
\mid {\color{lightgreen} x} \in V(G_1), \langle {\color{orange} y_1}, {\color{orange} y_2} \rangle \in E(G_2) \}.
\end{align} 
\end{matrix}\)
